snippet.title: The Callisto Protocol - Final Transmission Launch Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/the-callisto-protocol/

Experience Final Transmission, the heart-pounding final chapter of The Callisto Protocol.

The Biophage virus threatens to spread beyond the walls of Black Iron Prison. Fight through the derelict penitentiary in a last-ditch attempt to retrieve Mahler’s data, get it off Callisto and redeem yourself.

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games #callistoprotocolgameplay 

Rated Mature
